Env set-up:
-----------

0.  sudo yum install wget
1.  wget http://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.7.14/Python-2.7.14.tgz
2.  tar -zxvf Python-2.7.14.tgz
3.  cd Python-2.7.14
4.  sudo yum install gcc* -y
5.  ./configure
6.  make
7.  sudo make install
8.  wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
9.  sudo python2.7 get-pip.py
10. sudo pip2.7 install virtualenv

virtualenv setup:
-----------------

1.  virtualenv amazot
2.  source amazot/bin/activate
3.  sudo pip install slackclient

after slack bot creation

4.  export SLACK_BOT_TOKEN='your slack token pasted here'

edit print_bot_id.py to add token id and bot name

5.  python print_bot_id.py

If the abve doesn't work, then do "easy_install slackclient"

6.  export BOT_ID='bot id returned by script'
7.  sudo nohup python amazot.py &
